{"tid":2113265,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金管局再有助理總裁辭任","createTime":"2020-07-18T04:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T04:00:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d158ca32cf7b796a02f89a03d7184942c8634d62","tid":2113265,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200718/6Z6UAPDNPLFO4YGVSXPVZUN2DA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200718%2F6Z6UAPDNPLFO4YGVSXPVZUN2DA%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTicrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=955bcac1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200718%2F6Z6UAPDNPLFO4YGVSXPVZUN2DA%2F&h=9ed213ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200718/6Z6UAPDNPLFO4YGVSXPVZUN2DA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n金管局再有助理總裁辭任<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x1FZ9jdDvYXDb7WH025_4_og1TA=/639x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IGM234ADERVMRBKZDPMGS2HNMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx1FZ9jdDvYXDb7WH025_4_og1TA%3D%2F639x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIGM234ADERVMRBKZDPMGS2HNMU.jpg&h=a92ef7ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳家齊將升任金管局助理總裁。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】金管局昨公佈人事變動，未及50歲的助理總裁（貨幣管理）劉中健，因「個人理由」請辭，將於10月17日離任，是過去兩年來該局第四位離任的助理總裁級別高管。劉的原來職位則由外滙基金投資辦公室首席投資官陳家齊升任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉中健請辭 陳家齊繼任<br />\n<br />\n出身政務主任（AO）的陳家齊，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n畢業於港大法律學士的陳家齊，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於即將離任的劉中健，2018年3月才獲委任金管局助理總裁（貨幣管理），即升職未及兩年半便離任。該職位原本由鄭發出掌，惟鄭氏年僅50歲便於前年請辭，「過冷河」後加入會計師事務所工作。去年7月，同樣未夠50歲的助理總裁（外事）李永誠，亦因發展個人志趣請辭；另一前助理總裁（金融基建）李樹培，則於前年底離任，後來過檔中東擔任阿聯酋央行行長顧問。"}]}